      "raceComments": "{\"comment\":\"4. BLACK HAWK EAGLE comfortably disposed of two rivals on return last month at Chepstow (3200m) getting home by 2.25L. Looks to be little pace on here and could get away on the lead again. Leading fancy. 5. SHERBORNE is on a roll with recent victories registered in easy fashion. Handicapper hasn't let it go unnoticed but may not have caught up yet. Obvious claims. 3. COASTGUARD STATION now has a run under the belt for the new season. This is the time of year to catch him on previous evidence. Respect. 1. INSURRECTION will find this considerably easier than recent assignments with cheekpieces added. Revival needed however.\",\"runners\":[4,5,3,1],\"exclusive\":false}",
